{"sgc":false,"sfy":false,"qfy":false,"transUser":{"id":4170142,"status":99,"demand":1,"userid":455850871,"nickname":"汉城帝","uptime":1511706564341},"lyricUser":{"id":4170139,"status":99,"demand":0,"userid":64508574,"nickname":"芥末土豆焖饭","uptime":1511706564341},"lrc":{"version":46,"lyric":"{\"t\":0,\"c\":[{\"tx\":\"作词: \"},{\"tx\":\"Duncan Laurence\"},{\"tx\":\"/\"},{\"tx\":\"Jordan Garfield\"}]}\n{\"t\":1000,\"c\":[{\"tx\":\"作曲: \"},{\"tx\":\"Matte\"}]}\n[00:11.42]You have my heart\n[00:13.60]We'll never be worlds apart\n[00:16.73]Maybe in magazines\n[00:19.91]But you'll still be my star\n[00:22.91]Baby, 'cause in the dark\n[00:25.96]You can't see shiny cars\n[00:28.92]And that's when you need me there\n[00:31.95]With you I'll always share\n[00:34.96]Because\n[00:36.62]When the sun shine, we'll shine together\n[00:40.10]Told you I'll be here forever\n[00:42.73]Said I'll always be your friend\n[00:45.90]Took an oath and I'm stick it out till the end\n[00:48.63]Now that it's raining more than ever\n[00:51.90]Know that we still have each other\n[00:54.76]You can stand under my umbrella\n[00:58.20]You can stand under my umbrella\n[01:01.32](Ella, ella, eh, eh, eh)\n[01:04.85]Under my umbrella\n[01:07.02](Ella, ella, eh, eh, eh)\n[01:10.84]Under my umbrella\n[01:13.07](Ella, ella, eh, eh, eh)\n[01:17.18]Under my umbrella\n[01:19.45](Ella, ella, eh, eh, eh)\n[01:47.19]You can stand under my umbrella\n[01:49.86](Ella, ella, eh, eh, eh)\n[01:53.43]Under my umbrella\n[01:55.49](Ella, ella, eh, eh, eh)\n[02:00.04]Under my umbrella\n[02:02.31](Ella, ella, eh, eh, eh)\n[02:05.88]Under my umbrella\n[02:08.09](Ella, ella, eh, eh, eh)\n[02:13.32]These fancy things\n[02:15.27]Will never come in between\n[02:18.10]You're part of my entity\n[02:21.11]Here for infinity\n[02:24.08]When the war has took its part\n[02:27.16]When the world has dealt its cards\n[02:30.24]If the hand is hard\n[02:33.37]Together we'll mend your heart\n[02:36.48]Because\n[02:38.29]When the sun shines, we shine together\n[02:41.22]Told you I'll be here forever\n[02:44.09]Said I'll always be your friend\n[02:47.18]Took an oath and I'm stick it out till the end\n[02:50.44]Now that it's raining more than ever\n[02:53.52]Know that we still have each other\n[02:56.40]You can stand under my umbrella\n[02:59.77]You can stand under my umbrella\n[03:02.64](Ella, ella, ee)\n[03:06.30]Under my umbrella\n[03:08.36](Ella, ella, wueh)\n[03:12.49]You can stand under my umbrella\n[03:14.35](Ella, ella, eeh)\n[03:18.04]Under my umbrella\n[03:20.65](Ella, ella, eh, eh, eh)\n[04:14.39]It's raining\n[04:16.15]Ooh, baby it's raining\n[04:19.23]You can always come into me, come into me\n[04:26.13]It's raining\n[04:28.80]Ooh, baby it's raining\n[04:31.81]You can always come into me, come into me\n"},"klyric":{"version":0,"lyric":""},"tlyric":{"version":11,"lyric":"[by:汉城帝]\n[00:11.42]你占有我的心\n[00:13.60]我们永不分离\n[00:16.73]就算分隔两地\n[00:19.91]你仍是我的守护星\n[00:22.91]宝贝你如果处在黑暗中\n[00:25.96]你不会看到车灯闪烁\n[00:28.92]而当你需要我在这里时\n[00:31.95]我就会永远和你分享\n[00:34.96]因为\n[00:36.62]每当阳光照耀时,我们就共同发出光芒\n[00:40.10]承诺我会永远在这守候\n[00:42.73]我说过我会一直做你朋友\n[00:45.90]我发誓我会坚持到底\n[00:48.63]既然雨比以往还要猛烈\n[00:51.90]还好我们还拥有彼此\n[00:54.76]你可以站在我的伞下\n[00:58.20]你可以站在我的伞下\n[01:01.32](Ella ella eh eh eh)\n[01:04.85]在我的伞下\n[01:07.02](ella ella eh eh eh)\n[01:10.84]在我的伞下\n[01:13.07](ella ella eh eh eh)\n[01:17.18]在我的伞下\n[01:19.45](ella ella eh eh eh)\n[01:47.19]你可以站在我的伞下\n[01:49.86](ella ella eh eh eh)\n[01:53.43]在我的伞下\n[01:55.49](ella ella eh eh eh)\n[02:00.04]在我的伞下\n[02:02.31](ella ella eh eh eh)\n[02:05.88]在我的伞下\n[02:08.09](ella ella eh eh eh)\n[02:13.32]这些所谓新潮之物\n[02:15.27]从来都不会来我们中间\n[02:18.10]你是我存在的一部分\n[02:21.11]从咫尺到无穷\n[02:24.08]当战争造成了分离\n[02:27.16]当这个世界重新洗牌\n[02:30.24]就算无法改变\n[02:33.37]在一起我们抚平创伤\n[02:36.48]因为\n[02:38.29]每当阳光照耀时,我们就共同发出光芒\n[02:41.22]承诺我会永远在这守候\n[02:44.09]我说过我会一直做你朋友\n[02:47.18]我发誓我会坚持到底\n[02:50.44]既然雨比以往还要猛烈\n[02:53.52]就能知道我们还拥有彼此\n[02:56.40]你可以站在我的伞下\n[02:59.77]你可以站在我的伞下\n[03:02.64](Ella ella ee)\n[03:06.30]在我的伞下\n[03:08.36](Ella ella，wueh)\n[03:12.49]你可以站在我的伞下\n[03:14.35](Ella ella eeh)\n[03:18.04]在我的伞下\n[03:20.65](Ella ella eh eh eh)\n[04:14.39]雨正在下着\n[04:16.15]哦宝贝雨正在下着\n[04:19.23]只要需要，我的怀抱随时为你敞开\n[04:26.13]雨正在下着\n[04:28.80]哦宝贝雨正在下着\n[04:31.81]只要需要，我的怀抱随时为你敞开\n"},"romalrc":{"version":0,"lyric":""},"yrc":{"version":32,"lyric":"{\"t\":0,\"c\":[{\"tx\":\"作词: \"},{\"tx\":\"Duncan Laurence\"},{\"tx\":\"/\"},{\"tx\":\"Jordan Garfield\"}]}\n{\"t\":1000,\"c\":[{\"tx\":\"作曲: \"},{\"tx\":\"Matte\"}]}\n[11760,2190](11760,360,0)You (12120,390,0)have (12510,180,0)my (12690,1260,0)heart\n[13980,2850](13980,390,0)We'll (14370,360,0)never (14730,360,0)be (15090,540,0)worlds (15630,1200,0)apart\n[17070,2940](17070,780,0)Maybe (17850,300,0)in (18150,1860,0)magazines\n[20130,2700](20130,360,0)But (20490,270,0)you'll (20760,510,0)still (21270,360,0)be (21630,180,0)my (21810,1020,0)star\n[23100,3090](23100,810,0)Baby(23910,0,0), (23910,480,0)'cause (24390,330,0)in (24720,150,0)the (24870,1320,0)dark\n[26220,2970](26220,300,0)You (26520,450,0)can't (26970,270,0)see (27240,690,0)shiny (27930,1260,0)cars\n[29190,2700](29190,90,0)And (29280,390,0)that's (29670,300,0)when (29970,240,0)you (30210,570,0)need (30780,150,0)me (30930,960,0)there\n[32220,3030](32220,390,0)With (32610,450,0)you (33060,390,0)I'll (33450,630,0)always (34080,1170,0)share\n[35670,1530](35670,1530,0)Because\n[37200,2820](37200,180,0)When (37380,120,0)the (37500,360,0)sun (37860,540,0)shine(38400,0,0), (38400,240,0)we'll (38640,540,0)shine (39180,840,0)together\n[40200,2820](40200,450,0)Told (40650,390,0)you (41040,360,0)I'll (41400,450,0)be (41850,270,0)here (42120,900,0)forever\n[43170,2790](43170,600,0)Said (43770,330,0)I'll (44100,720,0)always (44820,360,0)be (45180,150,0)your (45330,630,0)friend\n[45960,3030](45960,240,0)Took (46200,210,0)an (46410,330,0)oath (46740,180,0)and (46920,120,0)I'm (47040,330,0)stick (47370,180,0)it (47550,240,0)out (47790,450,0)till (48240,240,0)the (48480,510,0)end\n[49350,2790](49350,390,0)Now (49740,240,